 1296   static const mxArray *emlrt_marshallOut(const char * u)
 1297   {
 1298     const mxArray *y;
 1299     const mxArray *m0;
 1300     y = NULL;
 1301     m0 = emlrtCreateString(u);
 1302     emlrtAssign(&y, m0);
 1303     return y;
 1304   }
 1305   
 1306   static const mxArray *b_emlrt_marshallOut(const uint32_T u)
 1307   {
 1308     const mxArray *y;
 1309     const mxArray *m1;
 1310     y = NULL;
 1311     m1 = emlrtCreateNumericMatrix(1, 1, mxUINT32_CLASS, mxREAL);
 1312     *(uint32_T *)mxGetData(m1) = u;
 1313     emlrtAssign(&y, m1);
 1314     return y;
 1315   }
